sentences.sContent: Some netizens are relentless in their resentment of her. Even her micro blog followers received warnings to stay away from the "quisling".
sentences.sContent_eng: Some netizens are relentless in their resentment of her. Even her micro blog followers received warnings to stay away from the "quisling".
sentences.sCn: 一些网民无情地对她发泄心中的怒火，她微博的一些粉丝甚至收到了警告，叫她的粉丝远离张铭依这个“卖国贼”。

trans.tranOther: someone who helps an enemy country that has taken control of their own country
